text: Yukhari-Karabakh economic region is one of 10 regions in Azerbaijan. Its administrative divisions are: * Aghdam (Ağdam) * Fuzuli (Füzuli) * Jabrayil (Cəbrayıl) * Khankendi (Xankəndi) * Khojaly (Xocalı) * Khojavend (Xocavənd) * Shusha (Şuşa) * Shusha (Şuşa) * Tartar (Tərtər) ==Related pages== *Economic regions of Azerbaijan ==References==
